"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:52.734375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/85b06/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/bc282/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/85b06/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/bc282/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/85b06/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/bc282/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/85b06/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/bc282/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/6925e59bec3de40aef02c7c7eaf435e1/f1720/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Our entire ad agency staff has a major soft spot in our hearts for all furry friends. That’s why we have such a passion at <strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\">The PM Group</a></strong> to support organizations who help animals in need. That’s how our relationship with God’s Dogs Rescue began. They have been one of the benefiting organizations at our annual Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala over the years, but we wanted to go further and make sure even more San Antonians know about the great work they were doing in our community.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why we chose to feature ‘<strong><em><a href=\"https://godsdogsrescue.org/\">God’s Dogs Rescue</a>’</em></strong> in our ‘<em>Making a Difference in San Antonio</em>’ article in SA INC on Valentine’s Day 2021 in the San Antonio Express News. Serving all of South Texas, God’s Dogs rescues &amp; fosters abused, abandoned, and neglected dogs until they can find their &#8216;furever&#8217; homes. Since 1995, God’s Dogs has been giving dogs a second chance in life in Texas, all over the country, and even in Canada!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>What a wonderful organization! The entire team at God’s Dogs has dedicated their lives to the rescue and well-being of our four-legged friends,</em>” stated PM Group founder and CEO Bob Wills. <em>“We are a very proud supporter of their mission,&#8221;</em> he added. &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for your next furry family member? Or maybe you and your family are wanting to become fosters to help organizations like God&#8217;s Dogs continue to have the helpful resources to find dogs their forever homes. Visit <strong><a href=\"https://godsdogsrescue.org/\">God’s Dogs website</a></strong> to learn more about how you can get involved and <a href=\"https://www.mysanantonio.com/sponsoredarticles/article/Making-a-Difference-in-San-Antonio-15954184.php\">check out the latest ‘Making a Difference in San Antonio’ feature.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 33 years now, the company has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profits, real estate and fitness. For two consecutive years now, the Agency has set best ever annual revenue records with the addition of six new clients and through the continued success of our existing clients. Additionally, the agency hosts their annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  In 2020 alone, the Agency donated over $1,050,000 to local non-profits. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Making a Difference in San Antonio: God’s Dogs Rescue","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Making a Difference in San Antonio: God’s Dogs Rescue","url":"/making-a-difference-in-san-antonio-features-gods-dogs-rescue/"}],"title":"Making a Difference in San Antonio Features God’s Dogs Rescue","metaDesc":"Our entire ad agency staff has a major soft spot in our hearts for all furry friends. That’s why at The PM Group we support organizations who help animals in need.","focuskw":"God's Dogs Rescue","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Making a Difference in San Antonio Features God’s Dogs Rescue","opengraphDescription":"Our entire ad agency staff has a major soft spot in our hearts for all furry friends. That’s why at The PM Group we support organizations who help animals in need.","opengraphImage":null,"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":{"altText":"God's Dogs Rescue Making a Difference in San Antonio - The PM Group San Antonio Advertising Agency","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image.png","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-300x158.png 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-1024x538.png 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image-768x403.png 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Gods-Dogs-Featured-Image.png 1200w"},"canonical":"/making-a-difference-in-san-antonio-features-gods-dogs-rescue/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"@id\":\"/making-a-difference-in-san-antonio-features-gods-dogs-rescue/#primaryimage\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"\",\"contentUrl\":\"\"},{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"/making-a-difference-in-san-antonio-features-gods-dogs-rescue/#webpage\",\"url\":\"/making-a-difference-in-san-antonio-features-gods-dogs-rescue/\",\"name\":\"